div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Task1-6\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformité de la ressource : unspecified </span>Task</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Ressource FHIR coeur</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/task.html\">Task</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Politique de référence</span><br/></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Résumé des interactions</span><br/><ul><li>Supporte <code>create</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Profils supportés</span><p><a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-task-transport-professionnel.html\">TDDUI Task Transport Professionnelversion : 2.4.0-ballot)</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-task-transport-usager.html\">TDDUI Task Transport Usagerversion : 2.4.0-ballot)</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-task-action.html\">TDDUI Task Actionversion : 2.4.0-ballot)</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-task-bilan.html\">TDDUI Task Bilanversion : 2.4.0-ballot)</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-task-moyen-ressource.html\">TDDUI Task MoyenRessourceversion : 2.4.0-ballot)</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-task-prestation.html\">TDDUI Task Prestationversion : 2.4.0-ballot)</a></p></div></div><p/></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"QuestionnaireResponse1-7\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformité de la ressource : unspecified </span>QuestionnaireResponse</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Ressource FHIR coeur</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/questionnaireresponse.html\">QuestionnaireResponse</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Politique de référe